<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>OTP Registration Email Template</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 30px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .header {
      text-align: center;
      color: #007bff;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .welcome-text {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #333333;
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .otp-code {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 15px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 1px dashed #007bff;
      color: #007bff;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .btn-verify {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .footer-text {
      color: #6c757d;
      font-size: 14px;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .footer-text a {
      color: #007bff;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">Welcome to Our App!</div>
    <div class="welcome-text">
      Hello, <strong><%= user.name %></strong>!
      <p>Thank you for registering with us. Please verify your email address to complete the registration process.</p>
    </div>

    <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 18px;">Your One-Time Password (OTP) for verification is:</p>
    <div class="otp-code"><%= activationCode %></div>
    <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 16px;">This OTP is valid for the next 10 minutes.</p>

    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="#" class="btn-verify">Verify Email</a>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-text">
      <p>If you did not request this OTP, please <a href="#">contact us</a> immediately.</p>
      <p>Thank you,<br>The [Your Company] Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>
